===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Lucas (Masters)}}
Lucas, who is based on [[Professor Rowan]]'s [[Professor's assistant|assistant]], in his {{game|Diamond and Pearl|s}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Dialga}}, {{p|Flareon}}, and {{p|Torterra}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Lucas became a playable sync pair on January 13, 2022.

Lucas has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. 

